{"tid":2021374,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[求幫忙尋game]遺忘咗十年前玩過嘅gane","createTime":"2020-05-17T16:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T16:57:38.000Z","uid":214129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ebc9374b43d8c41c7dc844ae47f9964bf31839ba","tid":2021374,"uid":214129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T16:36:04.000Z","msg":"話說自己十幾年前玩過一隻game，好想搵返隻game叫乜嘢名同睇返最後結局係點。因為太多年前所以冇乜記憶，求下勁人幫幫我手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想攞返啲回憶<br />\n<br />\n記憶中:<br />\n<br />\n1. PS1 or PS2嘅game嚟<br />\n2. 人物操控方式係好似GTA嗰個角度<br />\n3. 劇情我控制住隻角色打拳頭交順著劇情不斷打落去<br />\n4. 我要打好多充滿肌肉嘅boss<br />\n5. 隻遊戲係打人，拳頭交為主，唔係神話or妖魔鬼怪嗰啲劇情<br />\n6. 有一幕印象好深刻就係一間屋入面推開對大門，之後要打一個充滿肌肉嘅黑道boss、有一關係喺一個地下fighting club咁要一口氣打三個boss、 有一關係過咗一條橋，之後見到一座好大型嘅機械嘢，印像中好似要用鎖匙打開一道暗門，之後入去打唔知乜嘢再搞掂嗰座機械嘢、仲有一關係要同時打一個金色同一個銀色嘅大隻佬<br />\n<br />\n希望有人可以解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cdc9fea90d020a9a7774ee2b9691c5c72c1862f","tid":2021374,"uid":66546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T16:38:26.000Z","msg":"Crisis Beat?"},{"pid":"fcedb0fe00693e0f1f35fba4e298a8d9251fcb9d","tid":2021374,"uid":214129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cdc9fea90d020a9a7774ee2b9691c5c72c1862f","tid":2021374,"uid":66546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T16:38:26.000Z","msg":"Crisis Beat?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T16:45:43.000Z","msg":"google咗唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3f098c5c910bed91c1883b079c0a97b6cf2e09","tid":2021374,"uid":24592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"SAINTS ROW?"},{"pid":"b21a9092c58091cf5602b55ed22661297016f524","tid":2021374,"uid":316697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05